message: I added more history about the college, the campus and grounds that it is built on, and the academic opportunities that it presents to its students and listed some of its specialist programs. The edits made were to add more context to the school rather than one incident that occurred many years ago, I believe that the school deserves to have a fair chance and not just to be judged by one incident.
